  <p>Test passes if there is a <strong>horizontal green stripe</strong> below and <strong>no red</strong><tr><tr><tr>.
  </tr></tr></tr><div class=red></div>
  <table><div class=red><tbody><tr><td>&nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></div></table>
